⚠️ 5. Minor optional improvement
If a table entry is something like Westerlies or Westward Drift, your .includes(West) logic still works — which is great.
But if you ever add more complex wind models, you might want to normalize the strings:
const wind = we.primary.toLowerCase();
if (wind.includes(west)) ...



